short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Helps users import data from etoro.com to mrfin.app

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extensions allows you to export your eToro portfolio as a simple CSV.

To see data from eToro in Mr Fin you usually need to manually add your portfolio. This extension automates the process using one-click button.
